{{#> layout
  title='Translate Words and Learn Them with Flashcards'
  url='/'
}}
  <!-- Mashead header-->
  <header class="bg-light py-5">
    <div class='container-xxl py-5'>
      <div class='row align-items-center'>
        <div class='col-lg-5 order-md-last mb-5 mb-md-0'>
          <video
            id="promo-video"
            class="video-js vjs-fluid"
            controls
            width="640"
            height="264"
            poster="/assets/video-poster.png"
          >
            <source src="/assets/video.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
            <track label="English" kind="subtitles" srclang="en" src="/assets/video-subtitles.vtt" default />
            <p class="vjs-no-js">
              To view this video please enable JavaScript, and consider upgrading to a
              web browser that
              <a href="https://videojs.com/html5-video-support/" target="_blank"
              >supports HTML5 video</a
              >
            </p>
          </video>
        </div>
        <div class='col-lg-7 order-md-first'>
          <!-- Mashead text and app badges-->
          <div class='mb-5 mb-lg-0 text-center text-lg-start'>
            <h1 class='display-3 mb-5'>Translate new words while surfing the web and learn them on your mobile.</h1>
            <p class="text-xs-center text-lg-start">
              <a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/vocably/baocigmmhhdemijfjnjdidbkfgpgogmb" target="_blank"><img src="assets/available-in-the-chrome-web-store.svg" alt="Download on App Store" height="60" /></a>
            <div class="text-xs-center text-lg-start mb-5">
              <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/vocably-pro-language-cards/id1641258757" target="_blank" class="d-inline-block mb-2"><img src="assets/download-on-app-store.svg" alt="Download on App Store" height="60" /></a>
              <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.vocablypro" target="_blank" class="d-inline-block ms-2 mb-2"><img src="assets/get-it-on-google-play.svg" alt="Get it on Google Play" height="60" /></a>
            </div>
            <p class='lead fw-normal text-muted mb-5 me-lg-4'>If you want to master a new language, you must start using it. There is no other way. Vocably will support you in it by automatically creating high-quality flashcards based on the words you translated. You can review and learn your words in the mobile app when you have time.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- How it works-->
  <section id='how-it-works'>
    <div class='container-xxl'>
      <div class='h2 text-center text-lg-start mb-section'>How it works</div>
      <div class="row gy-4">
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <img class="img-fluid w-100 mb-4 mb-md-1" src="assets/img/how-it-works-01.svg" alt="Text selection">
          <div class="text-center lead my-2 d-none d-md-block">1</div>
          <p>Highlight an unfamiliar word while browsing any website on your desktop device.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <img class="img-fluid w-100 mb-4 mb-md-1" src="assets/img/how-it-works-02.svg" alt="Created flashcard">
          <div class="text-center lead my-2 d-none d-md-block">2</div>
          <p>Vocably will automatically convert the word to the normal form (i.e. infinitive for a verb or singular for a noun), get its definitions, translations, and create high quality flashcards.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <img class="img-fluid w-100 mb-4 mb-md-1" src="assets/img/how-it-works-03.svg" alt="Study cards on mobile device">
          <div class="text-center lead my-2 d-none d-md-block">3</div>
          <p>The created flashcards are available to be studied with Spaced
            Repetition System (SRS) method across all your mobile and desktop
            devices.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="pt-5 text-center d-none" id="chromeCta">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/vocably/baocigmmhhdemijfjnjdidbkfgpgogmb"><img src="assets/chrome.svg" height="32" class="pe-2" /> Try out Vocably Chrome Extension. It's free.</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <!-- Supported languages -->
  <section id='supported-languages' class='bg-light'>
    <div class='container-xxl'>
      <div class='h2 text-center text-lg-start mb-section'>Supported Languages</div>
      <p class='lead'>Vocably supports Arabic, Czech, English, German, Danish, Greek, Spanish, French, Hebrew, Hindi, Italian, Japanese, Korean, Dutch, Norwegian, Polish, Portuguese, Russian, Swedish, Thai, Turkish, Traditional Chinese, and Simplified Chinese.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
{{/layout}}

